high_descs: go to the sink
pick up the left most sponge from the sink
take the sponge to the stove
put the sponge in the pan on the back left burner
pick up the pan from the stove
take the pan to the counter left of the sink
put the pan on the counter
anns.task_desc: put a sponge in a pan and put the pan on the counter

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the left green sponge from inside the sink.
Turn around and walk to the stove on the right.
Put the green sponge inside the pan in the back left corner of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the sponge inside from the stove.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the pan with the sponge in the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a sponge on a counter.

high_descs: Turn right, head to the sink on the right.
Pick up the close sponge in the sink.
Turn around, bring the sponge to the stove on the right.
Put the sponge in the pan on the left of the stove.
Pick up the pan with sponge on the stove.
Bring the pan to the right, to the counter left of the sink.
Put the pan with sponge on the counter left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with sponge on the counter left of the sink.
